// >>> get_row((std::vector<std::vector<long>>({(std::vector<long>)std::vector<long>(), (std::vector<long>)std::vector<long>({(long)1}), (std::vector<long>)std::vector<long>({(long)1, (long)2, (long)3})})), (3))
